snippet.title: 7 Programming Podcast Episodes For Code Motivation
snippet.description:
7 Programming Podcast Episodes For Code Motivation

0:58 - The Tim Ferris Show, Ep. 125 Derek Sivers
3:11 - The Tim Ferris Show, Ep. 353 Patrick Collison
5:34 - The Artificial Intelligence Podcast, Ep. "Guido van Rossum: Python"
7:19 - The Tim Ferris Show, Ep. 36 Alexis Ohanian
9:02 - The Joe Rogan Experience, Ep. 1169 Elon Musk
11:07 - The Tim Ferris Show, Ep. 301Joe Gebbia
13:20 - The Artificial Intelligence Podcast, Ep. "Jeff Atwood: Stack overflow and coding horror"
